{"tid":975162,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"忽發奇想 有冇高手識整咁嘅app","createTime":"2019-01-09T12:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T15:59:00.000Z","uid":196856,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9bfdc993bdf8cc55a9e30aa8bcf5da5b70eba6e6","tid":975162,"uid":196856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:15:09.000Z","msg":"搭巴士嗰陣突然聞到好大陣食物味<br />\n心諗邊個咁冇公德心喺巴士食咁大味嘅嘢<br />\n但完全唔知喺邊度傳過嚟<br />\n想出聲屌柒條友都唔得<br />\n<br />\n所以突然間諗，有冇高手識整一隻app<br />\n係可以sense到有咩人喺同一架巴士<br />\n或甚係同一架公共交通工具，例如地鐵<br />\n<br />\n好多時我哋唔敢出聲係因為冇人幫<br />\n隻app就可以比我哋表態<br />\n例如覺得架車好陣食物味<br />\n或有人冇用耳筒大聲播嘢<br />\n跟著睇吓同一車廂有冇人認同自己<br />\n繼而可以合力屌柒條友"},{"pid":"8708563beea1f5e8584f9d859cae8d2a1bf3da24","tid":975162,"uid":192491,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:16:37.000Z","msg":"連登咪係"},{"pid":"897e1087a9ebafd5fb3a506ebd1ef23deac2de12","tid":975162,"uid":130897,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:17:56.000Z","msg":"屌柒人都要人幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc3dc790763554b9a99477a16deeade8edd1a9e","tid":975162,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:18:11.000Z","msg":"整個chat room收Bluetooth囉<br />\ngps實唔夠做<br />\n<br />\n利申唔識整"},{"pid":"fdb3b71d956e5d50089728efda74ea848df8f699","tid":975162,"uid":76747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:18:49.000Z","msg":"簡單"},{"pid":"7ee69d215c2c9b0f4d6ee85ea2f97bcd348b7ce7","tid":975162,"uid":196856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"897e1087a9ebafd5fb3a506ebd1ef23deac2de12","tid":975162,"uid":130897,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:17:56.000Z","msg":"屌柒人都要人幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 